  "notes": [
    "fact_work_items table serves both projector and reducer queues via stage column",
    "ProjectorQueue.Ack runs a 4-step transaction: supersede active generation, activate target, update scope, mark work succeeded",
    "InstrumentedDB decorates ExecQueryer with spans and pcg_dp_postgres_query_duration_seconds",
    "fact_records deduplication by fact_id before batching prevents Postgres ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE duplicate-key errors",
    "graph_projection_phase_state feeds reducer.GraphProjectionReadinessLookup for canonical_nodes_committed gating",
    "WorkflowControlStore persists workflow coordinator control-plane state with claim lease fencing",
    "Schema bootstrap in schema.go is ordered: each definition name must be unique; ApplyDefinitions is idempotent"
  ]
